# Step 5 — Egress check (tool: prom_query)
# Answers: is data flowing out of the platform, and to where?
# `<window>` = chosen window (default 7d). Both groupings sum to the same total.

# By event type (top types).
sum by (eventType) (increase(platform_egress_bytes[<window>]))

# By destination (e.g. eventwatch vs datalake).
sum by (dest) (increase(platform_egress_bytes[<window>]))
